    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n8351" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">σῆμα</span></b> , <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ατος</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">sign, token, mark</span>, by means of which
          anything is identified, <i><span class="en">Od. 23.188</span></i>;
          of the <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">mark</span> on a lot, <i><span class="en">Il.
            7.189</span></i>; a <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">spot</span> or <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">star</span> on a
          horse, <i><span class="en">Il. 23.455</span></i>; mark to show the
          length of a throw, <i><span class="en">Od. 8.195</span></i>; a sign
          from heaven, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">prodigy</span>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            21.413</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 13.244</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 22.30</span></i>; a <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">sepulchre</span>,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 2.814</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 7.86</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">characters</span> as a sort of pictorial
          writing, <i><span class="en">Il. 6.168</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
